Package com.stephengware.java.ai.planning.io

Contains objects for reading and writing objects in PDDL (Planning Domain Definition Language) format.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ObjectParser<E>
    An object parser provides a means of translating a node into an object of a specific kind.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    List
    A list is a collection of 0 to many nodes.
    Node
    The abstract parent class of List and Symbol.
    Parser
    Reads and parsed PDDL files to convert them into objects.
    Symbol
    A symbol is a string of characters.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FormatException
    A format exception is thrown when the input to a Parser is improperly formatted.
